           &kp CAPSLOCK  &trans  &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &trans    &kp EQUAL      &kp NUMBER_4  &kp N5        &kp NUMBER_6  &kp N0
&kp GLOBE  &trans        &trans  &kp LEFT_BRACKET      &kp RIGHT_BRACKET      &trans    &kp MINUS      &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &trans  &trans
